Bayan da kasar Sin ta fara aiki sosai a fannin kere kere, Amurka za ta ninka kudaden da ake kashewa wajen gudanar da bincike a wannan fannin, in ji mai saka jari da kuma mai binciken kere kere a kamfanonin Google, Microsoft da Apple, Kai-Fu Li.
Bayanan da aka yi a baya sun fara ne bayan wasu sassan gwamnatin Amurka sun ba da rahoton AI, duk da cewa Amurka ba ta da wata dabarar ci gaban AI.
A halin yanzu, China ta nuna shirinta na shekara ta biyu: tana son ta dauki matsayi na 1 a fannin kirkire-kirkire zuwa 2030.
"Ya kamata mu ninka kasafin kudin bincike kan AI, idan muka yi la'akari da cewa sauran kasashen sun yi nisa da Amurka, muna neman ci gaba a fannin AI", in ji Li.
Ƙarin tallafin kuɗi na biyu a kan babban buɗewa na gaba na IAI yana ƙara damar ci gaba a Amurka, "in ji Li a cikin hira da CNBC.
