A cikin shekarun 1980s ya yi aiki a kan tsarin AI a Jami'ar Carnegie Mellon, wanda ya kafa mafi girman rikodin a wasan Otello na Amurka, daga bisani ya zama babban daraktan Microsoft Research da kuma shugaban kamfanin Google na China.
Li ya san abubuwan da Amurka ta riga ta yi na fasaha, kamar su Defense Advanced Research Projects Agency's Robotics Challenge game da robotics, kuma ya tambayi lokacin da za a yi gasar ta biyu don taimakawa wajen gano mai zuwa.
