Yanzu suna kan gaba a cikin jerin, ƙungiyar da ba ta taɓa cin nasara ba a cikin masu fafatawa goma.
A ƙarshen wasan sun nuna kariya mai ban mamaki kuma, saboda haka, sun sami ikon sarrafa filin wasan, saboda haka kocin Peter Murchi yana da cikakken damar yarda.
Ko da yake muna da irin wannan wasa mai wuya, ba za mu iya yin watsi da shi ba, saboda haka ba za mu iya yin farin ciki ba, - wannan kocin.
