An fitar da katunan rawaya ga kyaftin din E, Blair MacPherson, kuma Melrouz bai yarda wani dan wasa ya karbi kwallon ba saboda Bruce Kolvin, saboda ƙarshen wasan ya kasance a ƙarƙashin matsin lamba.
