A San Diego, Lebron zai fara buga wasan farko a Layers
Masu sha'awar James Lebron na jiran sa a cikin 'yan wasa na Los Angeles Lakers.
A cewar kocin Lakers, Luke Walton, James zai yi wasa da Denver Nuggets a wasan bude kakar wasa a San Diego ranar Lahadi mai zuwa.
Amma ba a bayyana minti nawa da ya taka ba.
A shafin yanar gizon kungiyar an rubuta kalmomin Walton Fiye da minti daya, amma ƙasa da minti 48.
Wakilin 'yan wasan na Lakers Mike Trudel ya rubuta a shafinsa na Twitter cewa, "Wataƙila za a ba James ɗan lokaci kaɗan don yin wasa".
Bayan atisayen da suka gudana a farkon makon, James ya gaya wa dan uwansa game da shirinsa na wasanni uku na kakar wasa ta gaba.
Ya ce, "A wannan mataki na aiki, ba na bukatar in yi wasa kafin kakar wasa".
Kalli YouTube: Lokaci don taron Trump a West Virginia
Tun da yammacin yau ne birnin Willing na jihar West Virginia ke fara jerin tarurrukan da za a yi kafin zaben shugaban kasa Donald Trump.
Wannan taron na ɗaya daga cikin biyar da aka shirya, wanda ya haɗa da wurare masu zaman lafiya kamar Tennessee da Mississippi.
Bayan da aka jinkirta tabbatar da cewa shugaban zai kasance a zaben a Kotun Koli, Trump ya nemi taimako daga zaben tsakiya na gaba, saboda jam'iyyar Republican ta ƙuduri aniyar rasa jagorancin a majalisa idan za a jinkirta zaben zuwa watan Nuwamba.
Yaushe kuma ta yaya za a iya kallon taron Trump a West Virginia a kan hanyar sadarwa?
An sanar da cewa za a gudanar da taron ne a karfe 7 na yamma, ranar Asabar, 29 ga watan Satumba, 2018, a tashar Iti TuNaiT.
Za ku iya kallon taron Trump a West Virginia a cikin shirin live a cikin shirin da ke ƙasa.
Wataƙila an tilasta wa shugaban ya nemi Bretta Kavano, wanda ke zaune a Kotun Koli, saboda zargin da ake yi masa na yin jima'i ya sa yanayin ya yi tsanani; saboda haka an jinkirta zaben a cikin majalisar dattijai don tabbatar da hukuncin da zai faru, har zuwa mako guda, yayin da FBI ke gudanar da bincike.
Amma babban abin da ya fi damuwa a wannan taron shi ne, a taimaka wa 'yan Republican da suke fuskantar gwaji a zaɓen da za a yi a watan Nuwamba.
A wannan yanayin, an sanar da taron na biyar na mako mai zuwa don yakin neman zaben Trump don ƙarfafa masu ba da gudummawa da masu goyon baya, yayin da 'yan Republican ke ƙoƙarin haɓaka da kuma kiyaye jam'iyyarsu tare da mutane a cikin Majalisar Wakilai da Senate.
Wakilin yakin neman zaben Trump, wanda ya ki bayyana sunansa, ya shaida wa Reuters cewa: Shugaban kasa yana da matukar muhimmanci ga shugabancin majalisa, don haka a shirye yake ya ziyarci dukkan jihohi, kuma za mu shirya domin lokacin yakin neman zabe.
A cewar tashar West Virginia Metro News, A yau, masu goyon bayan Ohio da Pennsylvania da kuma kafofin watsa labarai na birnin Pittsburgh na iya halartar taron da za a yi a Wessbanco Arena a Wailing.
Trump, wanda ya shirya ziyarar ranar Asabar, zai kai ziyararsa ta biyu a watan da ya gabata a jihar ta West Virginia, inda ya samu sama da kashi 40 cikin 100 na kuri'un da aka kada a 2016.
An tilasta wa Trump ya goyi bayan dan takarar Senate na West Virginia, Patrick Morrissey, wanda ya shiga gasar Republican.
Wani masanin kimiyyar siyasa na jami'ar West Virginia, Simon Heder ya yi kira ga kamfanin dillancin labarai na Reuters cewa, ba zai yi kyau ba ga Morrissey da ya ga ya kamata shugaban kasa ya kara maka a takara.
Ryder Cup 2018: Ƙungiyar Amurka ta shirya don yin gwagwarmaya a ranar Lahadi a wasannin guda
Bayan wasanni uku a raga guda, gasar golf ta huɗu da aka yi a ranar Asabar ta kasance mai mahimmanci ga Ryder Cup.
Irin wannan zane-zane na canji na motsa jiki - an tsara shi sosai a cikin wasanni, amma musamman a irin wannan gasar 'yan wasa suna da tabbaci sosai.
Ina wannan babban al'amari yake yanzu?
Golfer Jordan Spit wanda ke hutu na rana ya ce: "Sun kasance maki shida a gaba, amma yanzu kawai hudu, saboda haka, saboda yanayin da ke sama, ba mu daina ba".
A cikin albitta, Turai ta yi nasara da maki 4, ta kai maki 12 a duk wasanni.
A cewar Spit, Amurkawa suna da ƙarfin zuciya da kuma motsawa a yanzu, saboda, alal misali, Spit da Thomas da suka yi wasa tare suna iya yin alfahari da maki uku da aka sanya daga hudu.
Daga farko zuwa ƙarshe, Spit ya kasance babban dan wasa mai ƙarfin zuciya.
A duk lokacin da aka buga wani abu mai mahimmanci a filin, ana yin murya a filin wasa, saboda Thomas ya yi yaƙi don maki biyu da ya rasa a baya.
A wasan da ya yi na kwanaki 15, an yi wa kwallo nasa waƙar murya a filin wasa. Sha'awar da golfer ke da ita ta nuna cewa yana da tabbaci ga tawagar Amurka.
"Ya kamata sauran su yi tunani sosai a yanzu kuma su damu da wasanninsu", in ji Spit.
Wannan shi ne abin da ya rage wa masu wasa su kula.
18 kawai bai isa ya bar alama a tarihi ba.
A cikin kwanaki biyu na ƙarshe, 'yan wasan Ryder Cup masu tarihi na Franchesco Molinaari da Tommy Flitwood sun wuce Spit da Tom da maki kaɗan.
Wadannan 'yan wasan golf biyu masu ban mamaki amma sanannun Turai suna da maki hudu daga cikin hudu, saboda haka duk abin da zai kasance mai kyau.
A cikin wasannin da Franchesco da Tommy suka yi a ranar Jumma'a da yamma da kuma Asabar da safe, ba su yi wani booggi ba (yawan bugun da ya kamata a yi a cikin gida ɗaya).
Idan Molinairi da Flitwood sun zama masu cin kofin Turai a ranar Lahadi a filin wasa na Golf na Nasonal, babu wasu 'yan wasan golf da suka fi su, domin suna da irin wannan ƙarfin da ke cikin hannayensu, a cikin kansu.
Kamar yadda aka yi tsammani, 'yan wasa biyu sun yi nasara a kan gidaje biyu.
Amma ga dukan Turai magana game da wani abu ne da wuri, watakila.
Bubba Watson da Webb Simpson sun yi nasara da sauri a wasan safe na hudu a kan jarumi Sergio Garcia, wanda ya taka leda tare da Alex Noren.
Garsio na Spain da Noren na Sweden sun kasance a baya saboda biyu dabbles tare da boggi guda biyu ((biyu fiye da bugun da ya kamata a yi a cikin gida daya).
A ranar Asabar, ba wanda zai iya taimaka muku.
Abin da ya fi ban sha'awa shi ne kallon 'yan wasan golf guda huɗu: yadda suke hulɗa da juna, waɗanne shawarwari suke bayarwa, waɗanne ne suke bi da waɗanne ba sa bi, musamman yadda ƙwarewar wasan take canzawa cikin ƙyar.
A gaskiya ma, akwai wasu sakamakon da suka fi kyau a Turai, misali, ta hanyar samun nasara a wasan karshe, amma wannan wasan hudu ya tabbatar da cewa Amurka tana da ƙarfin hali don yin gwagwarmaya, ko da yake ba su da imani a cikin jihohi.
Turai ta kai wasan karshe a gasar cin kofin Ryder da ci 10-6
Wasanni tsakanin 'yan wasa huɗu da suka faru a ranar Asabar sun sa Turai ta ci Amurka 10-6, kuma wannan babbar dama ce a gare su a wasan karshe na Ryder Cup.
Gwarzon dan wasan biyu Franchesco Molinairi da Tommy Flitwood sun ci Tiger Woods a filin wasa na Le Golf Naсьonale kuma sun kai ga maki hudu.
Kungiyar Turai ta Thomas Bjorn, wadda ke shirin lashe kofin farko, ta doke Amurka da ci 3-1 a wasan da suka yi da safiyar yau, bayan da suka yi watsi da shi a kulob din golf na Heseltaine shekaru biyu da suka gabata.
Duk da cewa ya ci wasanni biyu a cikin jihohi, amma ba su da isasshen maki.
Kungiyar Jim Furik tana bukatar maki takwas a wasanni 12 na mutum-mutumin da suka gudana ranar Lahadi domin ta ci nasara.
A tarihin gasar Ryder Cup, Flitwood shine farkon ɗan wasan golf na Turai da ya fara cin kwallaye huɗu a jere, yayin da yake tare da Molinari (wanda aka sani da Moliwood bayan wasannin hutu na ban mamaki) - kawai na biyu na biyu da ya ci kwallaye biyu a wasannin farko huɗu.
Bayan sun bar Woods da Patrick Reed a baya, sun kuma ci nasara a kan dan wasan farko na Amurka, Bryson Dechambon, da 5:4 da suka ci.
Woods, wanda ya buga wasanni biyu a ranar Asabar, ya yi nasara a wasanni 19 daga cikin 29 da ya yi a tsakanin mutane hudu, duk da cewa yana da lokacin da ya fi dacewa a cikin wasan.
Bayan wasan da ya yi na hudu da safe, Justin Rose, wanda ya ɗan huta, ya koma ga abokin aikinsa Henrik Stenson, kuma ya ci Dustin Johnson da Brooks Koepka da suka ci nasara a gasar ta duniya ta farko da ta uku da kashi 2: 1.
Ko da yake yanayin da ke kudu maso yammacin Paris yana da kyau kuma mai tsabta, ba za a iya cewa yanayin kungiyar Turai ba ne mai kyau.
Masu nasara a gasar uku, Jordan Spit da Justin Thomas, sun kafa wa Amurkawa alama ta biyu a ranar Asabar.
Sun yi nasara da John Ram da Jan Poulter na Spain da tsananin kokawa, suka ci 2:1, kuma daga baya suka dawo suka ci 4:3 a kan Polter da Rory Makilroy a cikin wasanni hudu.
A tarihin gasar Ryder Cup, sau biyu ne kawai ƙungiyar ta yi nasara a wasanni guda ɗaya da suka kasa da maki huɗu, kuma ƙungiyar Furic za ta iya samun nasara don riƙe kofin.
Idan sun zo na biyu a cikin kwanaki biyu, harin da aka kai ranar Lahadi ba zai zama kamar yadda suke ba.
Koriya ta Arewa ta ce ba za a taba samun sassaucin makamai ba tare da amincewa ba
Ministan harkokin wajen Koriya ta Kudu a ranar Asabar ya ce takunkumin da Amurka ke ci gaba da kakabawa Majalisar Dinkin Duniya zai kara tsananta wa kasashen amincewa da juna, saboda haka ba zai yiwu a ce ana maganar kare makaman nukiliya ba.
Ya yarda da cewa Ministan Ri Ён Ho ya sanar a babban taron shekara-shekara na Kungiyar Duniya, cewa Koriya ta Arewa ta yi muhimman ayyuka a shekarar da ta gabata: ta kammala gwajin makaman nukiliya da makamai masu linzami, ta dakatar da ayyukan da ke cikin tashar nukiliya, kuma ta yi alkawarin ba za ta yada fasahar nukiliya ba.
Amma ba mu ga amsar da ta dace daga Amurka ba  in ji ministan.
"Ba tare da amincewa da Amurka ba, ba za mu sami tsaro na kasa ba, kuma a cikin irin wannan yanayi ba za mu iya kawar da makamai ba".
Yayin da korafin Ministan Ri game da rashin amsawa daga Washington ga sauyin yanayi na Koriya ta Arewa ya zama sananne, an ji da'awarsa daidai, tun da Pyongyang a bara ta kasance mai tsayayya da rarraba makamai daga ƙasa ɗaya.
A cikin sakon nasa, Ri ya tunatar da yarjejeniyar da Shugaba Donald Trump da shugaba Kim Jong-un suka cimma a taron farko na hadin gwiwa a Singapore a ranar 12 ga watan Yuni, inda shugabannin kasashen biyu suka yi wa juna alkawarin cewa Koriya za ta fara aikin kare makamai, kuma Amurka za ta tabbatar da amincin su.
Koriya ta Arewa ta kai ga kawo karshen yakin Koriya na 1950-53, amma ta yi tsammanin Amurka za ta fara watsi da makaman nukiliya daga Pyongyang.
Washington, a nata bangare, ta yi kokarin sassauta takunkumin kasa da kasa mai tsanani da aka kafa kan Koriya.
Ri ya ce "Amurka ta nace kan kawar da makamai na farko kuma saboda haka har ma ta ƙi yin shelar ƙarshen yaƙi, ta hanyar matsa lamba daga takunkumin".
Sankuna mutane ne da suke mafarkin karya game da kawo mu ga kashin baya, ba su san kasarmu ba.
A gaskiya ma, takunkumin da ba a kawar da shi ba ya ƙara sa mu zama marasa imani.
Ri bai ce komai ba game da shirin taron kolin tsakanin shugabannin kasashen biyu da ke gaba da za a tuna da shugaban Amurka a Majalisar Dinkin Duniya.
A daidai lokacin, ministan ya yi magana game da tarurruka uku da suka faru tsakanin Kim da shugaban Koriya ta Kudu Moon Jae-in a cikin watanni biyar da suka gabata: Idan a wannan lokacin Koriya ta Kudu ta kasance a gefen cibiyar cibiyar maimakon Amurka, ba za mu sami matsala ba.
Amma, yanayin jawabin Ministan Ri ga Kungiyar ya sha bamban da na shekarar da ta gabata, inda Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ta tabbatar da cewa, ba a guje wa harin makamai masu linzami da Koriya ta Arewa ke kaiwa Amurka ba, saboda yadda Shugaba Trump ya kira shugaba Kim a baya mutumin makami mai linzami.
A wannan shekarar, a Majalisar Dinkin Duniya, shugaban Amurka, wanda ya yi barazanar "halaka Koriya ta Arewa gaba daya" a bara, ya yaba wa shugaba Kim don matakin da ya dauka na kawar da makamai, amma ya ce, idan ba a mayar da Koriya ta Arewa ba, takunkumi za su ci gaba da kasancewa, saboda haka dole ne a fara ayyukan da ke gaba.
A ranar Laraba, Trump ya ce babu wani lokaci da zai iya yin hakan:  Idan ya ba da shekaru biyu, uku ko watanni biyar ga wannan tambayar - ba kome.
China da Rasha sun yi magana da mai ba da shawara kan tsaro na Majalisar Dinkin Duniya game da bukatar ba da kyauta ga Pyongyang saboda matakan da suka ɗauka.
A halin yanzu, Sakataren Harkokin Wajen Amurka Mike Pompeo ya shaida wa mai ba da shawara kan tsaro na Majalisar Dinkin Duniya cewa, ya kamata a ci gaba da tabbatar da aiwatar da takunkumi daga bangaren Kwamitin Tsaro, ba tare da an kammala aiki na tsattsauran ra'ayi ba.
Tun daga 2006 Kwamitin Tsaro ya amince da tsaurara takunkumin da ya kafa kan Koriya ta Arewa, don haka ya yi kokarin dakatar da tallafin shirin nukiliya da makaman nukiliya na Pyongyang.
Ya gana da babban jami'in Majalisar Dinkin Duniya, Pompeo Ri, kuma ya sake zuwa Pyongyang a watan gobe don shirya taron na biyu.
Pompeo ya ziyarci Koriya ta Arewa sau uku a wannan shekarar, amma ziyararsa ta ƙarshe ba ta yi kyau ba.
Kuma a watan Yuli ya dawo daga Pyongyang, ya tabbatar da cewa yana da kyakkyawan sakamako, amma bayan 'yan sa'o'i kaɗan, sai Koriya ta Arewa ta zargi dan siyasar da yin wasu farillai masu haɗari.
A wani taro da aka yi a wannan watan, Koriya ta Arewa ta yi wa Moon alkawarin fitar da makaman nukiliya da makaman nukiliya idan Amurka ba ta dauki matakan da suka dace ba.
A cewarsa, ga Kim, waɗannan "matakan da suka dace" sun kasance kawai don tabbatar da tsaro a Singapore da Trump ya buƙaci, da kuma kyakkyawar sadarwa tare da Washington.
Darasi na hutawa mai kyau ga ɗaliban Harvard
Wani sabon darasi a Jami'ar Harvard ya tilasta wa ɗaliban dukan digiri na ƙarshe su yi barci sosai - wannan mataki ne da aka tsara don ya sabawa al'adun ɗalibai na shan kofi da dare ba tare da barci ba.
Wasu ɗalibai da suka yi karatu sosai a jami'ar da ta fi kyau a duniya ba su san yadda za su kula da kansu ba.
Farfesa a makarantar likita ta Harvard, masanin ilimin lissafi na jami'ar Brigham da asibitin mata da mata Charles Цейsler ya shirya wani darasi na musamman kuma a cewarsa, ba a taɓa samun irin wannan darasi a Amurka ba.
Ta yi wannan aikin ne bayan ta yi magana game da yadda rashin barci ke shafar karatu.
Bayan kammala karatun, wata yarinya ta zo wurin farfesa ta ce: Me ya sa nake jin wannan a farkon, a shekarar karshe kawai?
A cewar dalibi, babu wanda ya gaya masa muhimmancin barci, kuma hakan ya ba shi mamaki sosai, in ji mujallar Telegraph.
Wannan hanya ce ta farko da aka gabatar a wannan shekara, inda aka bayyana wa ɗalibai yadda barci ke taimakawa wajen karatu, wasanni, da kuma jin daɗi gaba ɗaya.
A cewar Paul Barreyra, farfesa a fannin ilimin halayyar dan adam na makarantar kiwon lafiya ta Harvard da kuma shugaban zartarwa na jami'ar, jami'ar ta yanke shawarar shigar da wannan darasi a cikin shirin bayan ta gano yadda dalibai suka kasa barci a cikin mako guda.
A cikin darasi na awa ɗaya, akwai abubuwa masu ban sha'awa da yawa, da kuma tambayoyi masu ban sha'awa.
Misali, a cikin hoton ɗakin kwana, ɗalibai suna nuna muhimmancin kafeyin da ke kan cokali, da kuma rashin barci, har ma da abin da za a yi kafin su kwanta.
Daga baya, ɗalibai suka yi nazarin yadda rashin barci ke kaiwa ga ciwon zuciya, bugun jini, baƙin ciki, har ma da ciwon daji.
Hoton wurin karatu tare da alamomi masu ma'ana, yana sa masu sauraron darasi suyi tunani game da yadda zasu ciyar da ranar.
Mun san cewa ba za a iya canza halin dalibai ba a yanzu.
Amma ya kamata su sami 'yancin sanin hakan - kamar yadda kuke da 'yancin sanin cutar da sigari ke haifarwa, "in ji Farfesa Цейслер.
A cewarsa, al'adun yin shiri don jarrabawa na dare yana cikin hamada, musamman ma fasahar zamani da kuma ci gaba da ci gaba da karatun da ke ci gaba da girma a kowace rana yana nuna cewa rashin barci shine babbar matsala.
Tabbatar wa ɗalibai muhimmancin samun isasshen barci zai zama abin da zai iya taimaka musu su guji damuwa, gajiya, da kuma gajiya, har ma da matsalar kiba - domin idan mutum bai samu isasshen barci ba, sai ƙwaƙwalwar mutum ta nemi ƙarin abinci.
Raymond So, ɗan shekara 19, wanda ya zo daga California, yana nazarin ilimin kimiyyar halitta da ilimin lissafi; bayan ya fara wannan darasi a farkon sa'arsa a bara, ya taimaka wa farfesa Цейсler ya tsara wannan darasi da kyau.
A cewarsa, ya ji daɗin darasin sosai har ya yanke shawarar yin darasi na ilimi na gama gari.
Fatansa, mataki na gaba shine tambayar daliban digiri na biyu game da yin wannan hanya kafin a sanya su a wasu wurare na ilimi.
Farfesa Цейsler ya shawarci ɗalibai su sanya sautin barci a lokacin kwantawa da lokacin tashi kuma kada su manta da cutar da allon shuɗi da fitilun haske.
