Mai kirkirar yanar gizo, ƙwararren kwamfuta Tim Berners-Lee, ya ƙaddamar da sabon farawa wanda ke fuskantar Facebook, Amazon da Google.
An gina aikin a kan dandalin Solid tare da lambar farawa ta Berners-Lee da ake kira Inrupt.
Solid yana ba masu amfani damar zaɓar inda za a adana bayanan su, wanda za su iya buɗewa ko bayar da bayanai.
A cikin wata hira ta musamman da ta yi da mujallar Fast Company, Berners-Lee ta yi dariya cewa burin Inrupt shine mamaye duniya.
