Labaran Redwater: Ƙarƙashin ƙwayoyin cuta a gundumar Pinella, Manati da Sarasota
Rahoton karshe na Hukumar Kula da Dabbobin Duniya da Kifi na Florida ya bayyana raguwar yawan ruwan ruwan ja a yankin Tampa Bay .
A cewar hukumar, an lura da yanayin korewar ruwa wanda ba a taɓa gani ba - raguwar maida hankali - a cikin yankunan Pinellas, Мэнати, Sarasota, Charlotte da kuma Kollier.
Red Water yana gudana a gefen bakin teku daga arewacin Pinellas zuwa yankunan Lee County kimanin kilomita 130.
Ana iya ganin irin wannan gurbataccen wuri a kusan mil 10 daga gabar tekun gundumar Hillsborough, amma ya ragu fiye da makon da ya gabata.
Irin wannan ruwan ruwan ja yana faruwa a gundumar Pasco.
A makon da ya gabata an bayar da rahoton matsakaitan taro a yankin Pinellas ko gabar tekun, ƙananan da manyan taro a yankin Hillsborough, ƙananan da manyan taro a yankin Мэнати, ƙananan da manyan taro a yankin Sarasota, ƙananan da matsakaitan taro a yankin Charlott, ƙananan da manyan taro a yankin Lee da ƙananan taro a yankin Collier.
Mutane a Pinellas, Manati, Sarasota, Lee da kuma Kollier County har yanzu suna gunaguni game da lalacewar numfashi.
A makon da ya gabata babu wani rahoton cutar numfashi a yammacin Florida.
